  • java.lang.Object

  • public class RapidTypeAnalysis
extends CGAnalysis
    Performs a Rapid Type Analysis (RTA) In terms of call graph construction precision this algorithm ranks better than CHA. Reference: https://courses.cs.washington.edu/courses/cse501/04wi/papers/bacon-oopsla96.pdf
    Author:
    Ben Holland
